message: The previous player's hint was very effective. Always combine three animals first to get a base value of 10. Then, apply the growth serum once (value usually jumps to 30-40). Next, use the mutation catalyst twice; the first time will drop the value to 0, but the second application will significantly raise it to around 75-85. Finally, use the growth serum a second time. This last step is a risk, sometimes raising the score to 90-95, and other times lowering it (e.g., from 85 to 65). If your score is already high (e.g., 80+) after the two mutation catalysts, you might consider submitting early to avoid the risk of the second growth serum. Avoid adding more than three animals or using tools more than the recommended times, as this consistently tanked the score.

I never used growth serum a second time, as the previous player's advice indicated it was a gamble and often not worth the risk once a high score was achieved with the mutation catalyst. Good luck!
